{"lemma":"قَضِيبَيْ","slug":"قَضِيبَيْ","root":"ق.ض.ب","root_slug":"ق-ض-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ض-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35829"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B6%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"branch or twig that has been cut off"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stick, rod, wand, staff"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"penis, phallus"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"rail (of a railroad)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"guide rail"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"birch (Betula gen. et spp.)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/qa.dˤiːb/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35829","headword_ar":"قَضِيبٌ","root":"qDb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", as an epithet applied to a branch,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqoDuwbN","text_ar":"مَقْضُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cut off"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fananN","text_ar":"فَنَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and Msb. *) ―         -b2-  And [as a subst.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rod, stick, wand, branch, twig, switch, shoot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stalk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guSon","text_ar":"غُصْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"branch from the stem"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from another branch, of a tree"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, M, O, Msb, K,) [and particularly]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is cut off:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quDobaAnN","text_ar":"قُضْبَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, O, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiDobaAnN","text_ar":"قِضْبَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, O, Msb, K, but this is less approved, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quDubN","text_ar":"قُضُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDobN","text_ar":"قَضْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a quasi-pl. n. (M, TA.) [Hence] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malaka Alburodapa waAlqaDiyba","text_ar":"مَلَكَ البُرْدَةَ وَالقَضِيبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became possessor of the burdeh and the rod"},{"kind":"text","text":"], meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ausotuxolifa","text_ar":"اُسْتُخْلِفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became a successor"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bow made of a rod,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"branch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its complete state:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one made of a rod,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"branch, not split:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) also called ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDobapN","text_ar":"قَضْبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b4-  And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quill"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a feather. (TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baTonN","text_ar":"بَطْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b5-  And (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"virga, nervus,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yard,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHát, T, K, TA,) of a bull, (AHát, TA,) or of a man, and of an animal other than man, (T, TA,) or of an ass, &c. (S, * TA.) ―         -b6-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A slender arrow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quDubN","text_ar":"قُضُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (As, TA.) ―         -b7-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A slender sword;"},{"kind":"text","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafiyHapN","text_ar":"صَفِيحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawaADibu","text_ar":"قَوَاضِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quDubN","text_ar":"قُضُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAth, TA:) or (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slender"},{"kind":"text","text":"as an epithet applied to a sword; (M, A, K; *) likened to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDiyb","text_ar":"قَضِيب"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the tree. (A.) ―         -b8-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaADibN","text_ar":"قَاضِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also (tropical:)  A she-camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has not been trained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broken-in:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has been ridden"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, M)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before she has been trained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"before she has been rendered gentle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that has not acquired expertness in being trained:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and applied also to the male. (M.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","O","Msb","K","AHn","T","TA","IAth","A"]}]}}